title: Pro Tools M-Powered Essential 8.0.3
description:
This software took me weeks to find as I didn't have the iLok and wasn't looking to buy one either. I have tested and am using this piece of software.

To install you can either use the image with (I like Virtual Clone) or you can burn this to disk. You will need an 8GB DVD.

You DO NOT need an iLok just a FastTrack USB or any other Hardware that is fully compatible.

This is the software that comes with the USB FastTrack.

Size is 7.9GB

Any questions, please just ask. 

Happy Downloading.

WinkleChops.


I dangle and they bite :P
